description:
You are a legal researcher. Research three landmark US Supreme Court cases: 'Gideon v. Wainwright' (1963), 'Miranda v. Arizona' (1966), and 'Tinker v. Des Moines' (1969). Create a Firefox bookmark folder named 'Constitutional Law' containing direct links to the case summaries for each. Document the official details for each case in a JSON file at '~/Documents/scotus_brief.json' with the following structure:
{
  "gideon": {
    "citation": "[U.S. Reports citation]",
    "date_decided": "YYYY-MM-DD",
    "vote_count": "[e.g. 5-4]",
    "opinion_author": "[Justice Last Name]"
  },
  "miranda": { ... },
  "tinker": { ... }
}
Ensure the vote counts and citations are exact.
